content.rendered:
Directed by Devanshu Singh. Satyanshu Singh

Written by Devanshu Singh. Satyanshu Singh

Cast Vinay Pathak (Madan Tiwary). Tillotama Shome (Sudha Tiwary). Seema Pahwa (Nani (as Seema Bhargava)). Khaled Masso (Hassan Mahdi). Bisha Chaturvedi (Lakshmi). Vedant Chibber (Chintu). Nate Scholz (Darren Reed). Reginald L. Barnes (Louis Jackson). Mehroos Mir (Waheed). Amina Afroz (Zainab).Marmar Alhilali.Mohamed Qasim Sainakh

Languages Hindi. English. Arabic

Producers Tanmay Bhat. Mayank Choudhary. Datta Dave. Chaitanya Hegde. Rohan Joshi. Gursimran Khamba. Naveed Manakkodan. Ashish Shakya
